{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "32d00d9c-791c-4332-8bdb-a31a9ff3523e",
    "name": "Magic Class Session 1 05 Runes",
    "sceneId": "981d126b-abc7-430a-abb4-e912340c59e6",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "8c390038-1b7b-4a52-837a-0fbe44443e7d",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "8c9a4afd-ce78-4927-8026-85fc264a2fb3",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "944e401a-ae04-4bf1-aaeb-9733451e1f7d",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Over the last two class sessions, you may have noticed how difficult it is to cast a simple spell. Visualizing runic symbols is not an easy task, particularly for non-Wizards such as yourselves.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "5ef2aa3a-aae3-4141-9dd5-a92ea5379c85",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Wizards commit hundreds of runes to memory and then have to mentally combine those symbols to cast their spells.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "36a7bdec-7a9b-49c6-91d8-6e2cb6429587",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "You undoubtedly found the task of casting multiple Sense Magic spells extremely wearying. It takes a good deal of energy to cast a spell.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "0cc34f12-f32b-4ca9-8d82-215b774cc4cc",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Magic would not be very practical to use if it exhausted a Magic User every time she tried to cast a spell. Therefore, we needed a method to make spellcasting easier.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "08c14add-f086-4bb3-a765-1670de23b50f",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, we will discuss runestones. These are small clay shapes inscribed with runic symbols and imbued with Mojo. When the Magic User concentrates upon the runestone, the spell is cast.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "e76b5848-9164-43e5-bc16-9cda3710b774",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "For instance, instead of memorizing the symbols for \"Magic\" and \"Perceive,\" we instead carved the symbols upon magical clay and baked the clay in a magical fire, we could create a Sense Magic runestone.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "91d12dcd-dd07-47fa-9996-59edb5f3a6e3",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "On one hand, having a Sense Magic stone would mean that you can cast the spell without getting tired. On the other hand, you must have the runestone in order to cast the spell.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "c631604c-aeee-4234-9c47-fc47708ded9d",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "We will be making runestones for all the other spells we learn in this class. Are there any questions about what I have discussed so far?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "5b8d023d-6a59-487e-a601-bf14a10a6fb5",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "820d5407-579c-4414-8c86-21580afb8e02",
                            "text": "Ask About Runestones and Non-Magic Users",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "edc52e03-fa68-4d8b-b56b-73fa260869c8",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "If runestones are magical, does this mean that anyone can use them, even non-magic users? Could we make extras to give away to our friends and family? ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "229a431b-3f62-42a2-b021-63b0ef510baf",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "That's very considerate of you to suggest that, Mr. O'Conner. Unfortunately, most runestones take some Mojo and concentration in order to evoke the spell from the runestone. Thus, only Magic Users can use them. While some Runestones can be created for non-magic users, they must be specially constructed.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "2bbf0921-1b7d-4877-8876-328932945f3e",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "29",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "3f95d08b-4acd-4e35-bd5d-605fc4fa99b1",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "e5195084-da79-4430-b190-abe215f0ab15",
                            "text": "Ask About Runestones and Different Spells",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "401a170a-daef-4b3a-9fee-d1732b262fae",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Can you put any spell on a runestone?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5115bff1-83e4-4107-b6f7-07848a046453",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "You can cast only simple spells from runestones. Many spells are far too complex to be confined to this method of spellcasting.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "e7663b27-51ef-415f-8a3d-df87daae91da",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "29",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "777baf00-4a7b-4d3a-8ae7-85f85da19764",
                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "ce7c9f68-99e3-4491-9542-450401327c02",
                            "text": "Say Something Snarky About Wizards",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5f1a8f31-2421-4793-9044-a7c4444bcba4",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Do Wizards live in towers because they always look down on everyone else?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "2446981c-f0b3-43f6-8d95-c6404e965586",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Wizards don't look down upon those who cannot wield magic... we just pity them. As for living in towers, well, towers are much sunnier and give a better view than living in a castle or a cave.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "29ebae68-362c-4486-82ec-31096feb1968",
